OL,3,CKamila Valieva: Russian figure skater
OL,4,Chanded four-year ban for doping
OL,6,FRussian figure skater Kamila Valieva
OL,7,Fhas been given a four-year doping ban
OL,8,Fand her results at the 2022 have been
OL,9,Fdisqualified.
OL,11,FValieva was initially cleared of
OL,12,Fbearing "no fault or negligence" for
OL,13,Ftesting positive for a banned
OL,14,Fsubstance (trimetazidine), during the
OL,15,FRussian national championships in
OL,16,FDecember 2021 - news of which emerged
OL,17,Fat the following year's Winter Games.
