OL,3,CKamila Valieva: Russian figure skater
OL,4,Chanded four-year ban for doping
OL,6,FBut Monday's verdict from the Court of
OL,7,FArbitration for Sport (CAS) overturns
OL,8,Fthat decision, after it ruled that
OL,9,FValieva had been unable to establish
OL,10,Fthat the anti-doping rule violation
OL,11,Fhad not been committed intentionally.
OL,13,FCAS confirmed all of Valieva's results
OL,14,Fsubsequent to the failed test had been
OL,15,Fexpunged and that she would have to
OL,16,Fforfeit any medals won during her
OL,17,Fperiod of disqualification, which
OL,18,Fwould include the team gold she won
OL,19,Fwith Russia in Beijing.
