OL,6,FThe United States finished second to
OL,7,FRussia in the team event, but CAS said
OL,8,Fthe power to strip the latter of its
OL,9,Fgold medal was "not within the scope
OL,10,Fof this arbitration procedure and will
OL,11,Fhave to be examined by the sports
OL,12,Forganisations concerned".
OL,14,FWere the United States to be promoted
OL,15,Fto the gold medal position, Japan -
OL,16,Fwho finished in third place - would
OL,17,Fretrospectively win silver and fourth
OL,18,Fplaced Canada bumped up into the
OL,19,Fbronze medal position.
