OL,3,CKamila Valieva: Russian figure skater
OL,4,Chanded four-year ban for doping
OL,6,FDespite news of her positive test
OL,7,Femerging after the team event, Valieva
OL,8,Fwas cleared to compete in the
OL,9,Findividual event, but failed to finish
OL,10,Fin a medal-winning position.
OL,12,FEven if she had secured a spot on the
OL,13,Fpodium, the International Olympic
OL,14,FCommitee (IOC) had stressed before the
OL,15,Findividual competition that medals
OL,16,Fwould not be awarded until a full
OL,17,Finvestigation had been completed.
