OL,3,CKamila Valieva: Russian figure skater
OL,4,Chanded four-year ban for doping
OL,6,FCAS said as part of its ruling that
OL,7,FValieva's age at the time of the
OL,8,Fdoping violation had no bearing on the
OL,9,Fsanction it should impose, and that
OL,10,Fthere is a burden on athletes of all
OL,11,Fages to prove there had been no
OL,12,Fintention to commit the violation.
OL,14,FValieva's four-year ban is backdated
OL,15,Fto the time of the failed test,
OL,16,Fmeaning it will run until Christmas
OL,17,FDay 2025.
