OL,11,FThe CAS decision is final and binding,
OL,12,Fbut parties in the case have the right
OL,13,Fof appeal to the Swiss Federal
OL,14,FTribunal within 30 days on limited
OL,15,Fgrounds.
OL,17,FValieva's legal team said it is
OL,18,Freviewing the CAS decision before
OL,19,Fdeciding whether to appeal to the
OL,20,FTribunal.
