OL,3,CKamila Valieva: Russian figure skater
OL,4,Chanded four-year ban for doping
OL,6,FHer lawyers had previously argued
OL,7,FValieva was contaminated by traces of
OL,8,Fthe trimetazidine medication they
OL,9,Fclaimed her grandfather used.
OL,11,FValieva, who turns 18 in April, has
OL,12,Fnot competed internationally since the
OL,13,FBeijing Olympics.
OL,15,FThe World Anti-Doping Association
OL,16,F(WADA) said it "welcomes" the CAS
OL,17,Fdecision, calling the doping of
OL,18,Fchildren "unforgivable".
