OL,3,CKamila Valieva: Russian figure skater
OL,4,Chanded four-year ban for doping
OL,6,F"Doctors, coaches or other support
OL,7,Fpersonnel who are found to have
OL,8,Fprovided performance-enhancing
OL,9,Fsubstances to minors should face the
OL,10,Ffull force of the World Anti-Doping
OL,11,FCode," a WADA statement read.
OL,13,F"Indeed, WADA encourages governments
OL,14,Fto consider passing legislation - as
OL,15,Fsome have done already - making the
OL,16,Fdoping of minors a criminal offence."
OL,18,FTravis Tygart, the chief executive
OL,19,Fofficer of the US Anti-Doping Agency
OL,20,F(USADA), said the CAS decision had
OL,21,F"been a long time coming".
