OL,6,F"We are incredibly pleased for clean
OL,7,Fathletes that this sad saga has
OL,8,Ffinally come to an end and hope they
OL,9,Fcan find joy and satisfaction in the
OL,10,Ffact that their long wait for justice
OL,11,Fis over," Mr Tygart said.
OL,13,F"At the same time, our hearts hurt for
OL,14,Fyet another Russian athlete who the
OL,15,Fsystem has failed.
